^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Okay, we will get to the 2C question in a second. But let's talk about this particular auction. First we will talk about Kerrie's bid. then hope's. What you should bid over the double Kerrie is 2S. Nada is showing hearts and spades. The rule is if there are 2 suits remaining on the way to NT, you bid the suit you have. 2S by Kerrie would show spades and deny hearts. But, regardless, 2N is a bit risky. Your other choices are pass and 3C. Pass is probably best. If you pass, Eddy bids 2H and I bid 2S (showing spades, asking about hearts), and then you can bid 3C. We might even stay out of 5C which is down 1.|
