Traditional HCPs|CP||FP||AT| in a hand are counted based on the standard formula of A = four points, King = three points, Queen = two points, and Jack = one point. Therefore, this hand|HT|q|cs|2|3d|5|at|^b  {|ih|psj73haKJdQj64cJ83|at|}|HT|t|AT|^k has 13 Traditional HCPs.|HC|sjhakjdqjcj|
